    "Numerous other reconstruction networks also consist of encoder and decoder components.",
    "Bergmann et al. [75] investigate the influence of structure similarity index measure (SSIM) and loss on AE reconstruction and anomaly segmentation, providing numerous suggestions for future research.How to resolve the difference between the reconstructed image and the original image is the most foundational principle.",
    "There are regularly differences in style between the reconstructed image and the original image, resulting in over-detection.",
    "Chung et al. [76] present an outlier-exposed style distillation network (OE-SDN) to preserve the style translation and suppress the content translation of the AE in order to avoid over-detection.",
